  <brief_title>Post-Marketing Surveillance Of Olmesartan Medoxomil In Combination With Hydrochlorothiazide</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Post Marketing Surveillance, Multicenter, Open-Label, Dose-Titrating, 4-Week Study Evaluating The Efficacy, Tolerability And Safety Of Olmesartan Medoxomil 20mg In Combination With 12.5mg Hydrochlorothiazide In Subjects With Stage 1 To Stage 2 Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
